title: Formula 1 2015 Japanese Grand Prix Full Race Sky 360p HEVC-[f1d]
description:
2015 Japanese Grand Prix Full Race

Free Practice sessions are all finished. Qualifying is done and dusted. The grid now assembles, slightly out of order thanks to Kvyat's massive Q3 shunt on Saturday. With Red Bull having to build the youngster a new car overnight, he's amassed a bunch of penalties.

Will the weather hold? Will the Mercs rain terror and domination on all those who would attempt to usurp the championship lead? Will Ferrari find their collective way to a stronger race than they've managed to show all weekend? And will Rossi get a chance to race at all, given that his Q1 lap was aborted due to Verstappen's Toro Rosso getting parked on the track?

All this gets answered in the next 5 hours.
